Description
AcceptanceCriteriaISCBusiness
The class manages the logic of the acceptance criteria for ISC type transactions, where you have a method that calls the ISC type data extraction method or calls the control method to check the status of the last transaction sent.
CharacterEncodingConversion
Class in charge of converting characters to hexadecimal ASCII or EBCDIC or from ASCII to text or from EBCDIC to text and from EBCDIC to ASCII.

Class in charge of calling the file upload service through an http request by a rest type call.
